c: 30
v: 30
t: "Naizvozvo, taridza (Muhammad (SAW)) chiso chako kuchitendero (cheIslaam) wova Haneef (uyo asinganamati chimwe chinhu kusara kwaAllah). Chitendero chaAllah, icho vakasikira vanhu. Pasave neshanduko pachitendero chaAllah. Ichi ndicho chitendero chakatwasuka, asi vanhu vazhinji havazvizivi"